title: september 3: eBay, beanie babies, and the dot-com bubble
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the beginning of early Internet giant, eBay, and the legends and facts around its founding. After, Maia explores more legends and facts -- this time about Frank Sinatra’s solo debut. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
